---
// ContinuaAprendizaje.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#f9f7f5] border-t border-slate-200/50 mt-12 mb-16 rounded-3xl" style="box-shadow: 0 -4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02), 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-6">Continúa tu aprendizaje</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-sans text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Obtener tus números personales es solo el primer paso. El despertar ocurre cuando comprendes el mensaje profundo que cada número del Árbol de la Vida guarda para ti.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hub de Enlaces -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <!-- L1 -->
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/lecturas-de-autoconocimiento-numerologia-cabalistica-y-arbol-de-la-vida/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#B11252]/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📖</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-[#B11252] transition-colors">Lecturas Personales</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Reserva tu sesión</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- L2 -->
      <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/70nLwpVOa8rsEOfjhRjlEE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#1DB954]/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🎧</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-[#1DB954] transition-colors">El Número del Alma</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Escuchar en Spotify</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- L3 -->
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#e6b866]/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🔮</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-[#e6b866] transition-colors">Blog Sabiduría de Alma</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Explorar el Blog</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- L4 -->
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/curso-basico-arbol-de-la-kabala" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-500/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🌳</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">El Árbol de la Vida</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Curso Principiantes</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- L5 -->
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/formacion-numerologia-cabalistica/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-500/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📚</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Formaciones Numerología Cabalística</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Ver opciones</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- L6 -->
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/lectura-completa-del-arbol-de-la-kabala-personal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#e6b866]/50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#B11252]/5 border border-[#B11252]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">✨</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-serif font-medium text-slate-800 group-hover:text-[#B11252] transition-colors">Levantar tu Árbol Personal</h4>
          <span class="text-sm font-sans text-slate-500 font-medium">Sesión 1 a 1 Integral</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
